  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735420/extras/1845ac25e6571f6250483578ac04cd99.poster.avif?t=1728938318\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735420/extras/1845ac25e6571f6250483578ac04cd99.webm?t=1728938318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735420/extras/1845ac25e6571f6250483578ac04cd99.mp4?t=1728938318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take care of the girls, clear their pipes, and unlock animated scenes! </h2><br><br><strong>Fake Hostel</strong> is a classic pipe puzzle game with lots of fun scenes and pleasing artwork. Move pipes around, complete numerous levels and reveal all our girls' secrets!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735420/extras/a89e116d214eaa9b2f9bc43ea97f3270.poster.avif?t=1728938318\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735420/extras/a89e116d214eaa9b2f9bc43ea97f3270.webm?t=1728938318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735420/extras/a89e116d214eaa9b2f9bc43ea97f3270.mp4?t=1728938318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735420/extras/833e1c32fbef7cf332375c1296010d7b.poster.avif?t=1728938318\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735420/extras/833e1c32fbef7cf332375c1296010d7b.webm?t=1728938318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9